f=Engineering/dev/custom/delivery-governance/assets/definition-of-done.md · h1:Definition Done dev/delivery-governance=change DONE box checked. claim "done" unchecked boxes returned gaps named. operator explicitly accept gap logged tech debt agent never silently downgrades "done." · h2:The gates (all required)=**Reviewed** code-review-standards passed (correctness security tests style), **Tested** quinn's required tiers present; assertions meaningful; fragile-area regression applicable, **Gated** quinn's release gate green (tiers regression Reticle verdicts Playwright suite), **Secured (if risky)** new external surface auth data path aegis passed, **Charter-clean** external-tool calls plan-locked (Rail 1); agent-run destructive (Rail 3); sandbox respected (Rail, **Documented** ADR architecture decision made; stack-profile updated stack changed, **Rollback-ready** ops confirms tested rollback exists (no deploy without one) · h2:Tech-debt register (append-only)=\| Date \| What was deferred \| Why \| Risk \| Trigger to fix \| · h2:Tech-debt register (append-only)=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · h2:Branching / merge=[Per stack-profile. Default unset: review green gate linear/revertable history.]